	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Motaba Virus</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_HELP">
			<Text>Our military intelligence has brought in a babbling medic, who claims to have discovered an incredibly dangerous virus while doing charity work in one of the far-flung corners of the world.[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]Only this man's research need make it to our Science Advisor...</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Enemy cities experience biological terrorism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Gain {2_InstantYield}. Your cities become immune to biological terrorism.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Gain 2 Guided Missiles in every city.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Your Aircraft gain the Air Siege III promotion.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Get me the head of CI:6. I'm authorising the use of this virus against civilian populations.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>What are you talking about?! This is horrifying. Send the Doctor to our best Medical Lab, we need to be prepared should this thing ever break loose!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>This is just what the boys over at prototype weapons have been looking for. Green light the Scud Storm project.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_MOTABA_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>We can't trust something like this to those nutjobs over in RnD. Get me the Airforce.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
